# Wrapper Classes and Collections

Collections in Java store only objects.

## Example

```java
import java.util.ArrayList;

class Demo {
    public static void main(String[] args) {

        ArrayList<Integer> list = new ArrayList<>();

        list.add(10);
        list.add(20);

        System.out.println(list);
    }
}
```

